  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of RESC study is to assess the efficacy of Energetic Resonance by Cutaneous
      Stimulation on alcohol withdrawal symptoms measured by CUSHMAN score and in a second time to
      measure the benzodiazepine amount prescribed during the withdrawal time.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
